    <fields>
        <fullName>Callista_External_Id__c</fullName>
        <description>Holds a concatenation of the Callista Person Id (from &apos;Contact.Person_Id_unique__c&apos;), and underscore(&apos;_&apos;), and the Course Code (from &apos;Course__c.Name&apos;). This is a unique combination (for academic courses).</description>
